{"tid":877545,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"要錢唔要貨？德福花園劈27%　呎價滑落至1萬元水平","createTime":"2018-10-26T12:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T13:23:04.000Z","uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f601be5cf55a23cc2bfa1dfdf3fc91bc62b2b0ec","tid":877545,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181026/photo/bkn-20181026143736034-1026_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181026181239\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181026143736034-1026_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181026181239&h=0486995d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n二手樓市終於出現「要錢唔要貨」的一幕！向來認為抗跌力較強的市區大型屋苑，剛有大手劈價的成交。<br />\n<br />\n香港置業譚征透露，上述為九龍灣德福花園T極低層單位，實用面積474方呎，8月時叫價690萬港元，屬鎖匙盤，且已交吉，至9月時已減至630萬元，前晚業主突然通知，可以減價至550萬元，最終劈至500萬元低價售出，呎價僅約10,549元。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，單位位處極低層，加上內籠無裝修，新買家購入後需要翻新，但成交價亦無理由低至上述水平。據了解，有大型銀行對單位估值仍逾620萬元。<br />\n<br />\n德福花園屬港鐵站上蓋屋苑，樓價向來被看高一線，而實用面積近500方呎單位，高峰時售價曾達800萬元；而有極低層單位，面積亦400餘方呎，年中登記成交價亦達550萬元。"},{"pid":"bab70b48a2ff411907c1b72b1ce08de79bd2e2a1","tid":877545,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/26/201813_4c3ade940ab50d9fc1c49d9370b16ee6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F26%2F201813_4c3ade940ab50d9fc1c49d9370b16ee6.png&h=34ee43b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31861ca0459cc53ec2a9cf6df1d96c630d895a0e","tid":877545,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T12:40:38.000Z","msg":"但成交價亦無理由低至上述水平<br />\n<br />\n跌就跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a60687a95701ed59a72b361a1edfc61e4fc028","tid":877545,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"484=近500呎"}]}